narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: I think that my only complaint would be that the computers we have at our desks aren't powerful enough to run some of the grasshopper scripts we came up with. Consequently, they were a bit of a limiting factor in terms of our final output.
